[{"id":"RAW_2b1e7283","title":"Claude Code 创始人再次公开：团队的 10 个使用技巧！","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyNjM2MzQyNg==&mid=2247718904&idx=1&sn=7f77ee06ab57fd11bc44ab6f782cd644","date":"2026-02-03 14:58:00","oneSentenceSummary":"Claude Code 创始人 Boris Cherny 分享了团队内部提升 AI 编程效率的 10 个进阶技巧，涵盖并行工作流、规则固化及子智能体应用。","summary":"本文由 Claude Code 创始人 Boris Cherny 总结并分享了其团队内部使用该工具的 10 个核心技巧。文章强调了 AI 辅助编程不应仅停留在简单的对话层面，而应通过工程化手段提升效率。核心建议包括：利用 git worktree 实现多任务并行处理；在复杂任务中坚持“计划先行”并引入 Review 机制；通过持续迭代 CLAUDE.md 文件来固化项目规范；封装自定义 Skill 以处理技术债和上下文聚合；以及利用 Subagents 增加算力投入和任务卸载。这些技巧旨在帮助开发者构建更高效、更自动化的 AI 协作工作流。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_2b1e7283.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Datawhale","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":10,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_f186294d","title":"深度解读：OpenClaw 架构及生态","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzNjE2NTI3NQ==&mid=2247491455&idx=1&sn=33d58cb6f0d2cd3b9c08c3c84a223e25","date":"2026-02-02 23:05:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_f186294d.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"浮之静","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":56,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_8fb9eeb9","title":"解构 Clawdbot：本地架构、记忆管理、Agent 编排与上下文组装原理","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2NDU4OTExOQ==&mid=2247694343&idx=1&sn=8974e62e0c74a0011c6fdf6d037f957c","date":"2026-02-03 00:45:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_8fb9eeb9.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"腾讯云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":27,"score":93},{"id":"RAW_bc19b98b","title":"从传统编程转向大模型编程","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&mid=2247558172&idx=1&sn=4352d94bba884ceac8f3f231a9074910","date":"2026-02-03 00:30:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_bc19b98b.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"阿里云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":42,"score":93},{"id":"RAW_df4d1702","title":"生产级 Prompt 自动化推理评估 A/B 实验结